5: I know. I said, I know! I'll do it!

right?

I never claimed to want such a
thing! In fact, I clearly remember
being entirely unwilling
113:

125:
Somewhere I know you can't wait to
be.
133:
Nope, you're not getting outta this.
We're gonna get you to have some

141:

I'm actually curious about that

230:
